- File system structure
   |
   +-- README (file, optional)
   |     This file, just for information.
   |
   +-- crl-<name> (folder, e.g. crl-mycrl1, one for each CRL)
       Two examples are contained.
       - Folder crl-download-mycrl2 (name is download-mycrl2)
         CRL will be downloaded automatically.
       - Folder crl-provided-mycrl1 (name is download-mycrl1)
         CRL will be provided via out-of-band mechanism.
